Cargo is the package manager. 

Packages are referred to as crates.

Command to create a new rust project and repo named hello_cargo
cargo new hello_cargo 

Build the cargo project
cargo build 

Build and run a project in one step 
cargo run

make sure you can build the code, but don't actually build it 
cargo check

manually compile a rust file
rustc <file>

format your rust files automatically
rustfmt


